To learn the alien words I watched mostly the second symbol, which in most of the cases resembled me the shape of the objects, like the vase with holes, I associated that with water, so the drop and being it open most of the symbols where open or the cactus thing was shaped like a y so like a alphabet letter so in the alien word there was the L (I know it doesn’t make much sense but it made to me)
Because I learned only some of the symbols per word when in the final part of the experiment the words not in the central part of the screen I had difficulties recognising them.
I really enjoyed this study
